---
import ContactSection from '../components/ContactSection.astro';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Our Services">
    <section class="animate-fade-up pt-36 pb-16 px-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto -mt-24" style="--delay: 100ms">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold font-headline mb-8 text-on-surface tracking-tight">Our Services</h1>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg md:text-xl font-light leading-relaxed max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                We build dedicated systems tailored to the client's unique needs. Our service includes a wide range of Activities: Establishment and maintenance of computer networks, information security solutions, software maintenance and maintenance CAD, handling and maintenance of security focal software, etc.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 auto-rows-auto md:auto-rows-[300px]">
            
            <!-- Service 1: Network Design -->
            <div class="md:col-span-8 md:row-span-2 bento-card shadow-[0_20px_40px_rgba(0,104,87,0.06)] flex flex-col p-10 bg-surface-container-lowest overflow-hidden border border-outline-variant/30">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-8 relative z-10">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold font-headline text-on-surface mb-4">Network Design</h3>
                        <p class="text-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl leading-relaxed font-medium">We’ll meet with you to get a full understanding of your current network design and business operations to find a solution that strikes the right mix of performance and value.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-grow grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 opacity-80 mt-8 relative z-0">
                    <div class="flex flex-col justify-end">
                        <div class="h-40 bg-surface-container rounded-t-xl relative overflow-hidden">
                            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-primary/20 h-4/5"></div>
                            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-primary h-1/2"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col justify-end">
                        <div class="h-56 bg-surface-container rounded-t-xl relative overflow-hidden">
                            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-primary/20 h-full"></div>
                            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-primary h-3/4"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col justify-end">
                        <div class="h-32 bg-surface-container rounded-t-xl relative overflow-hidden">
                            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-primary/20 h-2/3"></div>
                            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-primary h-1/3"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Service 2: Data Security Solutions -->
            <div class="md:col-span-4 md:row-span-1 bento-card bg-primary text-white p-10 relative overflow-hidden shadow-xl shadow-primary/20 flex flex-col justify-between">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl mb-4" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">security</span>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline mb-3">Data Security Solutions</h3>
                    <p class="text-primary-fixed/90 text-md leading-relaxed">Use flexible data security solutions that will decrease IT risks and increase continuity and stability for your business operations.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Service 3: Professional Software Maintenance -->
            <div class="md:col-span-4 md:row-span-1 bento-card relative overflow-hidden group bg-gradient-to-br from-[#001712] to-primary/20 border border-primary/10">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#001712] via-[#001712]/80 to-transparent p-10 flex flex-col justify-end z-10">
                    <h3 class="text-white font-bold font-headline text-2xl mb-3">Professional Software Maintenance</h3>
                    <p class="text-emerald-100/90 text-[15px] leading-relaxed font-light">
                        Fractal Provides Maintenance Services in Software Management , Request Based Software Services, Maintenance Services For Third Party Software
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Service 4: Security Company Solution Maintenance -->
            <div class="md:col-span-4 md:row-span-1 bento-card bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 flex flex-col justify-between hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors border border-outline-variant/30">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">policy</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-headline text-on-surface mb-3">Security Company Solution Maintenance</h3>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-[15px] leading-relaxed">Our specialists will assess your network and recommend a customized solution that delivers reliable information security and gives your business the freedom to work safely and efficiently.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Service 5: Network Solutions -->
            <div class="md:col-span-4 md:row-span-1 bento-card bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 flex flex-col justify-between hover:bg-emerald-50 transition-colors border border-outline-variant/30">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">hub</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-headline text-on-surface mb-3">Network Solutions</h3>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-[15px] leading-relaxed">Whether you need a network service partner that knows how to build a reliable network solution, or need someone to improve your existing network, FRACTAL has the expertise to get you there.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Service 6: Support Consulting -->
            <div class="md:col-span-4 md:row-span-1 bento-card bg-primary-fixed/20 p-8 flex flex-col justify-center text-center border border-primary-fixed/30 hover:bg-primary-fixed/30 transition-colors">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-xl shadow-primary/30">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">support_agent</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline text-primary mb-3">Support Consulting</h3>
                <p class="text-[15px] text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">We have certified computer technicians on staff to offer fast, friendly, expert service. With our remote access tools, we can often fix your problem right from our office – no need to travel to your place of business</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Exact Contact Us Section from user specification -->
    <ContactSection lang="en" />

</Layout>
